Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:22.74,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356,660)\fs80}克林特\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h伊斯特伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:34.45,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\t(0,600,\fs136)\pos(960,670)\c&HDAF2FF&}荒野大镖客
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,又是你 给我滚出去！\N{\ren}You? You again! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,按我说的去做 滚出去！\N{\ren}Do what I told you. Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑！看老子怎么教训你\N{\ren}Go on! Run! I'll teach you to keep away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快滚！\N{\ren}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸！\N{\ren}Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你这狗杂种！\N{\ren}You filthy dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,拿钱来赎你老婆啊\N{\ren}You'll settle with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\ren}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,「再见了 老兄」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎你 陌生人\N{\ren}Welcome to you, stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫胡安·迪欧斯 是个撞钟人\N{\ren}My name is Juan de Dios. I am the bell ringer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你来此贵干？见罗霍家族吗？\N{\ren}Why are you here? To see the Rojos?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不是罗霍家族的话 难道是巴克斯特家族？\N{\ren}No, not the Rojos. Is it the Baxters maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至也不是巴克斯特家族\N{\ren}Maybe not even the Baxters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你想发财 是吗？\N{\ren}You want to get rich, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你若肯用脑\N{\ren}Well, for that you have come to the right place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那可就来对了地方了\N{\ren}If you use your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这里的人要么发达\N{\ren}That's because everybody here has become very rich...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要么死掉\N{\ren}or else they are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你想买什么？枪？酒？\N{\ren}What do you want to buy? Some guns? Liquor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是买家 是卖家 卖线索来换黄金\N{\ren}You don't buy. You sell. You sell lead in exchange for gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里你要么发达 要么死掉\N{\ren}You will get rich here, or you'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我又要敲丧钟了\N{\ren}Juan de Dios tolls the bell once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊 这位朋友\N{\ren}Saludos, amigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,离家漂泊可不明智啊\N{\ren}It's not smart to go wandering so far from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他是选错路了\N{\ren}I reckon he picked the wrong trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,或是选错了地方\N{\ren}Or he could have picked the wrong town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 他最大的错是投错了胎\N{\ren}His big mistake, I think, was getting born.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你如果想找工作  而又穿成这样\N{\ren}If you want any work, lookin' like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可以试试当稻草人\N{\ren}you could try bein' a scarecrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,得了吧 乌鸦都可以把他吓尿\N{\ren}Oh, no, the crows are liable to scare him maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\ren}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\ren}Saludos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样是不会发达的\N{\ren}You can't get rich like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,顶多 你会被人干掉\N{\ren}At most, you will only succeed in being killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我们这里的麻烦 我们只能靠你了\N{\ren}With all of the trouble we have, all we needed was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-要点什么？-食物和喝的东西\N{\ren}-What are you looking for?  -Food and something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-水在那边  -不 不要水\N{\ren}-Water's over there. -No, no water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,吃饱喝足 然后杀人\N{\ren}Eating and drinking and killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你的能耐仅此而已 你们这种人都一样\N{\ren}That's all you can do, just like the rest of your kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我要赊账\N{\ren}By the way, you'll have to mark this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 你没有钱\N{\ren}I know. You have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟 你刚到镇上\N{\ren}After all, you just got into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但你若不在乎杀人的话\N{\ren}But if you don't mind doing a little killing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,会有很多人乐意付钱请你的\N{\ren}You will have no trouble finding someone eager to pay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就连我的轮盘赌也被卖掉了\N{\ren}My roulette wheel. That, too, was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没人来这里玩了\N{\ren}No one ever comes here to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这的人把时间都花在丧葬上了\N{\ren}We spend our time here between funerals and burials.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,从没见过这么死气沉沉的小镇\N{\ren}Never saw a town as dead as this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远找不出第二个这样的小镇\N{\ren}You will never see another like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-这里到底怎么了？-这里充斥太多杀戮\N{\ren}-What's wrong with the place?  -We've had too many killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看到那些女人了吗？\N{\ren}You have seen the women?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她们不是女人 是寡妇\N{\ren}None of them are women. They're widows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方只有寡妇\N{\ren}The place is only widows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 只有杀人才能得到尊敬\N{\ren}Here you can only gain respect by killing other men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以再也没人工作了\N{\ren}So nobody works anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看来有人不同意你的观点\N{\ren}Seems somebody doesn't share your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛\N{\ren}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\ren}Saludos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,知道皮里佩洛为什么会看你吗？\N{\ren}Know why Piripero looked you over?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是在量你的尺寸\N{\ren}To take your measurements.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他经验丰富 只看一眼就够了\N{\ren}He is so experienced. he can do it with a glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你会光顾他的\N{\ren}You will be a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:09:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,别笑 我不是在说笑\N{\ren}Don't laugh. I'm not joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我警告你 那些歹徒总有一天会干掉你\N{\ren}I want to warn you that those murderers will make a corpse out of you one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想让你离开这里\N{\ren}That's why I want you to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想呆在墓地里吧\N{\ren}You don't want to stay in this cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,吃完就离开吧\N{\ren}Finish up and get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说过我没钱\N{\ren}I told ya I can't pay ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,算我请客\N{\ren}Be my guest...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,离开圣米格尔 好吗？\N{\ren}but get out of San Miguel, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这通向哪里？\N{\ren}Where does that lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,阳台\N{\ren}The balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你去上面干什么？喂\N{\ren}Why are you going there? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就看看\N{\ren}To have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在高处俯瞰 总会有不同的发现\N{\ren}Things always look different from higher up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是上面什么都没有\N{\ren}But nothing's up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快点离开吧！\N{\ren}Go ahead and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是谁？\N{\ren}Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,强盗 强盗和走私犯\N{\ren}Bandits. Bandits and smugglers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们从德克萨斯来的\N{\ren}They come down from Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:11:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们穿越边境来囤积枪和酒\N{\ren}They cross the frontier to stock up on guns and liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的成本比较低\N{\ren}The cost is much less here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们回去把枪和酒卖给印第安人\N{\ren}Then they go back and sell the guns and liquor to the Indians.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,每个卖枪和酒的城镇都会致富\N{\ren}Any town that sells guns and liquor has gotta be a rich one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不是城镇致富 是买主卖主致富\N{\ren}Not the town, only those who buy and sell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那些老大才是挣巨额利润的人\N{\ren}and the bosses are the ones who clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？总得有人掌管这里 每个城镇都有个老大\N{\ren}Yeah? Somebody has to run the place. Every town has a boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 但当这个城镇有两个老大的话...\N{\ren}That's true, but when there are two around...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一山不容二虎\N{\ren}then I'd say that there is one too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,两个老大\N{\ren}Two bosses?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思\N{\ren}Very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,确实有意思\N{\ren}Interesting is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这边是罗霍家族 三兄弟兜售烈酒\N{\ren}The Rojos boys, three brothers who sell liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那边是巴克斯特家族 大军火贩\N{\ren}And then there's the Baxters, big gun merchants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我没搞错的话  你已跟巴克斯特的人碰过面了吧？\N{\ren}If I'm not mistaken, you already met Baxter's gang, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 见过了\N{\ren}Yeah, we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你真走运 他们很少只对骡子开火\N{\ren}But you're lucky. They don't usually limit their fire to the mule.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,每当一个男人背井离乡 来此处转悠\N{\ren}A man leaves his own land and looks around for any reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,胡安·迪欧斯就会敲一下钟 皮里佩洛就会多卖一副棺材\N{\ren}Juan de Dios tolls the bell and Piripero sells another coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,两个老大\N{\ren}Two bosses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们招募边境两边所有无所事事的人渣\N{\ren}They've enlisted all the scum that hangs around both sides of the frontier...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,以美元支付酬劳\N{\ren}and they pay in dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,巴克斯特家族在那边\N{\ren}The Baxters over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,罗霍家族在那边\N{\ren}The Rojos there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在中间\N{\ren}Me right in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你想干什么？\N{\ren}Where you do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,敲钟的疯子是对的\N{\ren}Crazy bell ringer was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个可以发财的好地方\N{\ren}There's money to be made in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我猜对你想干的事 我劝你还是别尝试\N{\ren}If you're thinking what I suspect, I tell you, don't try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们两边谁比较厉害？\N{\ren}Which one of the two is the stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们两边谁厉害？\N{\ren}Which one of them is stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,罗霍家族 尤其是雷蒙\N{\ren}Well, the Rojos, especially Ramon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,米格尔·罗霍阁下 我想跟你谈谈\N{\ren}Don Miguel Rojo, I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:13:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,米格尔阁下 我听说你在招募成员\N{\ren}Don Miguel, I hear you're hiring on men.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能很适合\N{\ren}Well, I might just be available.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在你雇佣我之前 我想告诉你\N{\ren}I gotta tell you before you hire me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我要价可不便宜\N{\ren}I don't work cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,准备三副棺材吧\N{\ren}Get three coffins ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了 老兄\N{\ren}Adios, amigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 异乡人 你还不明白吗？\N{\ren}Listen, stranger! Didn't you get the idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不想在镇里看到你这种人\N{\ren}We don't like to see bad boys like you in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快找你的骡子滚吧\N{\ren}Go get your mule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你让它跑了吗？\N{\ren}You let him get away from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我正想跟你们谈这事\N{\ren}That's what I want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-它现在心情低落  -谁？\N{\ren}-He's feeling real bad. -Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的骡子\N{\ren}My mule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你们开枪射它的蹄子 使它受了惊\N{\ren}He got all riled up when you men fired those shots at his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你在说笑吗？\N{\ren}Hey, are you makin' some kind of joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\ren}Eh, No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们只是玩玩而已\N{\ren}I understand you men were just playin' around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是骡子...它不了解\N{\ren}But the mule... He just doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 如果你们道歉的话\N{\ren}Of course, if you were to all apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还笑 我觉得这样很差劲\N{\ren}I don't think it's nice, you laughin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我的骡子不喜欢别人笑它\N{\ren}My mule don't like people laughin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦笑它 它就会发狂\N{\ren}He gets the crazy idea you're laughin' at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们若肯道歉  我知道你们会的...\N{\ren}Now, if you apologize, like I know you're going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我会说服它 你们不是故意的\N{\ren}I might convince him that you really didn't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我都看到了 你把他们四个都杀了\N{\ren}I saw the whole thing. You killed all four of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你会付出代价 会被绞死的\N{\ren}You'll pay all right. You'll be strung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\N{\ren}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,别开枪\N{\ren}Don't fire a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫约翰·巴克斯特 是警长\N{\ren}I'm John Baxter, sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？你是警长的话\N{\ren}Yeah? Well, if you're the sheriff,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,最好把这些人埋了\N{\ren}you better get these men underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我错了 应该是四副棺材\N{\ren}My mistake. Four coffins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你我要价不便宜\N{\ren}I told you I wasn't cheap...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但你会发觉是物有所值的\N{\ren}but I think you'll find it's worth your while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,97 98 99 100\N{\ren}97, 98, 99, 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的等成事后再给\N{\ren}The rest when you're all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么时候开始？\N{\ren}When do I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,至少现在我还不急\N{\ren}I'm not in a hurry, at least for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,巴克斯特少了四个成员 现在正是大好时机\N{\ren}I'd say with four less Baxters, right now is as good a time to start as any.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说几天后 有一队骑兵会经过这里\N{\ren}In a few days I hear there will be a troop of cavalry passing through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望军队插手我们的生意\N{\ren}I wouldn't want the military sticking their long noses into our business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你的消息很灵通\N{\ren}You seem to be well informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种地方 要活命就得靠小道消息\N{\ren}In these parts, a man's life often depends on a mere scrap of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这玩意儿对使用者来说派不上什么用场\N{\ren}This thing couldn't have been very useful to its owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我弟弟雷蒙做的 他经常拿它做射击训练\N{\ren}My brother Ramon did that. He often uses it for target practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他手中有枪 就无人敢挡\N{\ren}With a gun in his head, no one stands in his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这副盔甲是他最喜欢的靶子之一\N{\ren}The suit of armor is one of his favorite targets...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 是当他没别的东西可射击时才用\N{\ren}Naturally when he does not have anything better to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我还真有点想会会你这位弟弟了\N{\ren}Well, I'll be kind of curious to meet this brother of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是奇科 我最信任的手下之一\N{\ren}This is Chico, one of the most trusted of my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他走 他会带你去你的房间\N{\ren}Follow him. He will bring you to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你有回到自己家的感觉\N{\ren}I would like you to feel at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没有自己家 不过还是走吧\N{\ren}Well, I never found home that great, but let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她是谁？\N{\ren}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫玛丽索尔 你最好别打她主意\N{\ren}Her name's Marisol. You just forget about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的房间\N{\ren}This one will be your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你给了他100美元\N{\ren}You gave him $100.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从没付过这么多钱\N{\ren}We never pay that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你能解释你为什么要雇用他吗？\N{\ren}Can you explain to me why you have taken him on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,让那个恶心的美国佬白吃白住 还给他100美元？\N{\ren}To have that filthy gringo around the house and to give him $100 besides?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从来没给过那么高的价钱\N{\ren}We have never paid anybody so much
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能让那种人在这里为所欲为\N{\ren}You cannot leave someone like that to do what he wants around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他什么事都做得出来\N{\ren}He's capable of doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而我只想要这里井然有序\N{\ren}And I want law and order in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你只要这些  那我有更便宜的办法\N{\ren}If that is all you want, there is a much cheaper way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,做了他\N{\ren}Just snuff him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来动手呢？你吗？\N{\ren}And who would be the one? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有何不可？\N{\ren}Yes, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,朝他背后开一枪就能解决所有麻烦\N{\ren}A shot in his back, then you would have him out of the way in no time at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我现在可以轻易得手\N{\ren}Listen, I could do it easily right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他无法预料 我还可以取回那一百元\N{\ren}He won't be expecting it, and I'd get back the hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你真蠢 伊斯特班 即便是兄弟我也敢骂你\N{\ren}You are stupid, Esteban! Even if you are my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,背后放冷枪就解决问题？\N{\ren}A bullet in the back, eh? And it is ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那万一你手抖射偏了呢？\N{\ren}And what happens if your hand should tremble slightly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,万一他只是受了点伤呢？\N{\ren}And he's only hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,骑兵队就要来了 那美国佬拔枪又特别快\N{\ren}And with the cavalry arriving in town and that Yankee so quick on the draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-我只是想...  -你别瞎想了\N{\ren}-I was only thinking... -You mustn't think of anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来做主\N{\ren}You let me do the thinking instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看那个美国佬 问他需要些什么 跟他交个朋友\N{\ren}Go and see the americano. Just ask him if he needs anything and make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我听清楚\N{\ren}Get one thing clear in that head of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在雷蒙回来之前 镇上不能节外生枝\N{\ren}This is going to be a quiet town until Ramon gets back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？不能节外生枝\N{\ren}Is that clear? A quiet town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我是伊斯特班·罗霍 我哥哥叫我...\N{\ren}I am Esteban Rojo. My brother asked me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢？\N{\ren}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,搬走\N{\ren}Moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道不知道所有手下得跟我们一起住吗？\N{\ren}But didn't you know all our men live here with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是很舒适 但我发现你们并不是都很欢迎我\N{\ren}That's all very cozy, but I don't find you men all that appealin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,再说了 你哥哥说现在用不着我\N{\ren}Besides, your brother said he didn't have any need for me anymore right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,立定\N{\ren}Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-军士？-什么事 长官？\N{\ren}-Sergeant. -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,传令今晚我们驻扎此地\N{\ren}Tell the men we'll be spending tonight here in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,安排他们来这里领取补给\N{\ren}Arrange it so they can pick up the supplies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 加倍守卫 看好马车\N{\ren}Also, double the guard in order to watch the stagecoach there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,0:21:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官\N{\ren}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜那马车上装着什么？\N{\ren}What do you suppose they're carrying in that coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很容易查明\N{\ren}It'd be easy to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,走近看清楚就行了\N{\ren}Get up close to it and take a little look at what's in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们向你开枪 那么里面就是金子\N{\ren}If they fire at you, you know it's gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:21:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这主意不赖啊\N{\ren}Not a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在找什么？\N{\ren}Looking for anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\ren}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,走开 美国佬\N{\ren}Get out of here, Yankee.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么没睡呢？\N{\ren}Why aren't you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你这样瞪着 我很不安\N{\ren}When I see you staring like that, it bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我还在想那马车里有什么\N{\ren}I still keep wondering what was in that stagecoach.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是他们认为很重要的东西\N{\ren}It's something they seem to think is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我随口问了几个问题  队长差点要抓我\N{\ren}I asked a few questions of the captain and almost was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽索尔是什么人？\N{\ren}Who's Marisol?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好睡会儿 你会需要的\N{\ren}You better get some sleep. You need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是你 也太危险了\N{\ren}It's much too dangerous, even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.34,0:23:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是问她是谁\N{\ren}All I did is ask who she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一个女人\N{\ren}She is a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙爱她爱疯了\N{\ren}And Ramon's madly in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.51,0:23:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,现在明白了吧？\N{\ren}Does that make it clear to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,镇里的每个人都谈论雷蒙\N{\ren}Everybody in this town talks about Ramon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真想会会他\N{\ren}Kind of curious to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你够聪明的话\N{\ren}If you are smart, you will try to stay
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就尽可能远离雷蒙\N{\ren}clear of Ramon as long as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那些军人正悄悄地前进\N{\ren}There are the soldiers. They are moving on very quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪\N{\ren}Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:23:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是往边境前进\N{\ren}They're headed for the frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我\N{\ren}Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.24,0:24:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你每晚都是这样睡觉的吗？\N{\ren}is that the way you go to bed every night?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.60,0:24:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 我不会弄脏被单的\N{\ren}Don't worry. I didn't dirty the sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我也去\N{\ren}Wait. I'm coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.35,0:24:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我要看看你是怎样惹祸上身的\N{\ren}I want to see for myself how you're going to get yourself in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.94,0:24:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了 走吧\N{\ren}All right. All right. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.11,0:25:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就像玩老鹰捉小鸡一样\N{\ren}It's like playing cowboys and Indians.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.49,0:25:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-上尉  -欢迎 中尉\N{\ren}-Captain. -Welcome, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.78,0:25:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这是答应给你的黄金\N{\ren}There's your gold as promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.37,0:25:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你给我们的枪械 对军队一样有用\N{\ren}I hope the guns you will be giving us will be equally useful to our army.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.04,0:25:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,请放心 上尉 我们一起验货\N{\ren}Rest assured, Captain. We'll check them over together.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.27,0:27:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快给他们换上衣服\N{\ren}Get their clothes on again, and hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.64,0:27:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,务必把尸首安置好\N{\ren}Be sure to place them around right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.65,0:27:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了 他们是互相残杀的\N{\ren}Remember. They died fighting among themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.10,0:27:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,卢比奥！\N{\ren}Rubio!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.18,0:27:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看到没 他就是雷蒙\N{\ren}There. It's Ramon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.52,0:27:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的弟弟雷蒙\N{\ren}This is my brother Ramon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.19,0:27:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我提过他了\N{\ren}I think I mentioned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.18,0:27:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,人人都在谈雷蒙\N{\ren}Everybody talks about Ramon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.04,0:28:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也有很多人提到你 包括我亲爱的兄长\N{\ren}And many speak of you, too, my dear brother included.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.33,0:28:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,希望他们说的是好话\N{\ren}Well, I hope they say nice things.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.12,0:28:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,旅程愉快吗？\N{\ren}Did you have a good trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.54,0:28:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,很累\N{\ren}It was tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.54,0:28:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大白天赶路酷热难耐\N{\ren}It was terribly hot on the road during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.84,0:28:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,坐马车也不舒服\N{\ren}And stagecoaches are an uncomfortable way to travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.97,0:28:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定你很快就恢复了\N{\ren}Well, I'm sure you'll be in great shape in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.26,0:28:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,美国佬等不及要行动了\N{\ren}The americano cannot wait to get into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.97,0:28:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 恐怕要让他失望了\N{\ren}I am sorry. He's going to be a disappointed man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.38,0:28:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\ren}How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.62,0:28:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,巴克斯特接受了邀请 他们今晚赴约 米格尔阁下\N{\ren}The Baxters accepted the invitation. They'll come tonight, Don Miguel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.44,0:28:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,巴克斯特来这里？你疯了吧\N{\ren}The Baxters coming here? You must be out of your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.62,0:28:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是我吩咐奇科邀请他们的 他听从我的命令\N{\ren}Chico followed my orders. I told him to invite them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.91,0:28:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙 这是怎么回事？\N{\ren}Ramon, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.41,0:28:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在旅途之中我领悟了很多事\N{\ren}I have found out many things when I was traveling...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.54,0:28:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们两边这样火拼下去 没完没了\N{\ren}and I have decided that it's very stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.28,0:28:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是非常愚蠢的\N{\ren}to just keep on shooting at each other and without any results.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.54,0:28:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了 雷蒙\N{\ren}You've gone out of your mind, Ramon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.01,0:28:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我很理智 伊斯特班\N{\ren}No, I have come to my senses, Esteban.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.26,0:29:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\ren}Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.42,0:29:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\ren}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.01,0:29:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,生命很宝贵\N{\ren}Life can be so precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.20,0:29:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,浪费每一分钟都很愚蠢 不是吗？\N{\ren}It's foolish to risk losing it every minute, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.10,0:29:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这个镇子很大 足以容纳每个人\N{\ren}There's plenty of space for everybody in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.11,0:29:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,包括巴克斯特家族\N{\ren}Even Baxters, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.19,0:29:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,因此...\N{\ren}For this reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.45,0:29:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定放下武器\N{\ren}I've decided to hang my gun up on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.04,0:29:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得雷蒙说得对\N{\ren}I think that Ramon has the right idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.24,0:29:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也厌倦了打打杀杀 是时候停战了\N{\ren}I, too, am getting tired of these killings. They must stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.14,0:29:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这些话让人非常感动\N{\ren}This is all very, very touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.94,0:29:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说你不赞赏和平？\N{\ren}You mean you don't admire peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.20,0:29:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,让一个人去喜欢他不了解之事 是很难的\N{\ren}It's not real easy to like something you know nothing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.26,0:29:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,呆在圣米格尔 你会学到很多东西的\N{\ren}Stay in San Miguel and you may just profit from the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.93,0:29:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不了 谢谢 我要走\N{\ren}No, thanks. I'll be movin' on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.48,0:29:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的钱 米格尔阁下\N{\ren}Here's your money, Don Miguel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.03,0:29:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我只花了一点儿\N{\ren}I only used a small amount of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.34,0:30:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我无功不受禄\N{\ren}I don't like to take money unless I feel I've earned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.96,0:30:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛急着走？你应该呆在这里\N{\ren}Now, why are you so hasty? You should stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.10,0:30:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以和我们共享晚餐\N{\ren}You might enjoy dining with us tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.12,0:30:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我 巴克斯特失去四个手下\N{\ren}The Baxters have four men in the cemetery on account of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.64,0:30:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他们不希望我在场\N{\ren}I don't think they'd appreciate my presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.26,0:30:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢那个美国佬 作为雇佣枪手 他聪明过头了\N{\ren}I don't like that americano. He's too smart to be just a hired fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.68,0:30:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-但他枪法无人能比  -我看得出来\N{\ren}-At shooting a gun no one can touch him. -I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.56,0:30:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一副嘴脸的人以枪谋生 你可以料到两件事情\N{\ren}When someone with that face works with his gun, you may count on two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.60,0:30:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他枪法神速 机智过人\N{\ren}He's fast on the trigger, but he's also intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.60,0:30:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这种人太危险了 兄弟们\N{\ren}That makes him too dangerous for you, I think, my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.39,0:30:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,既然他走了 你能解释一下那番白痴言论吗\N{\ren}Now that he's gone, will you please explain that silly nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.04,0:30:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什么放下武器 和巴克斯特家族和解？\N{\ren}about hanging up your gun and making up with the Baxters?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.74,0:30:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 有没有可能\N{\ren}Is it possible, old fellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.68,0:30:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远无法自己得出任何结论？\N{\ren}that you'll never be able to reach any conclusions on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.50,0:30:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道认为政府和美国佬一旦发现尸体后\N{\ren}Don't you think our government and the americanos will find those bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.88,0:30:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不会展开调查吗？\N{\ren}and then start an investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.92,0:31:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就让他们调查\N{\ren}They'll investigate, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.64,0:31:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们暂且沉寂 和平地度过这段时间\N{\ren}and we'll be quiet and peacefully abide our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.96,0:31:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对于里奥·布拉沃的大屠杀一无所知 是吧？\N{\ren}We know nothing about the massacre at the Rio Bravo, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.72,0:31:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我故意把尸体排列成\N{\ren}I arranged for the bodies to be lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.94,0:31:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,自相残杀而亡\N{\ren}as if both companies killed each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.35,0:31:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但你认为他们会相信吗？\N{\ren}But do you think they'll believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.02,0:31:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为他们会\N{\ren}Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.61,0:31:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因为若他们找不到凶手...\N{\ren}Because if they don't find some guilty party...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.78,0:31:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就自然会放弃调查\N{\ren}It would be a pretty good reason to call off the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.20,0:31:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 那巴克斯特家族呢？\N{\ren}Yes, but what about the Baxters?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.99,0:31:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,巴克斯特家族？\N{\ren}The Baxters?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.10,0:31:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就想着和平共处\N{\ren}They want nothing more than to live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.83,0:31:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们暂时让他们为所欲为\N{\ren}We'll let them have their own way for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.38,0:31:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,别管巴克斯特家族了\N{\ren}Forget about the Baxters.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.76,0:31:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,调查结束之后我们再好好招待他们\N{\ren}We'll take care of them later when the investigation finishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.30,0:31:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你那个主意真不错\N{\ren}That was a fine idea that you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.04,0:31:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么来着？\N{\ren}What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.06,0:31:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是了 是了\N{\ren}Ah, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.81,0:32:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,巴克斯特家族在这边 罗霍家族在那边\N{\ren}The Baxters are on one side. The Rojos on the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.28,0:32:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你就在中间\N{\ren}And you'd be in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.90,0:32:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是他们结盟了\N{\ren}The only problem is that they've joined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.99,0:32:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你找不到工作了\N{\ren}Now you are without a job,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.48,0:32:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有钱付你的帐了\N{\ren}and you don't have money to pay me what you owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.16,0:32:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在只有一个选择 赶紧离开这里\N{\ren}There is only one thing for you to do. Leave here immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.80,0:32:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以不计较你欠的钱\N{\ren}I will forget about what you owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.96,0:32:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,离开圣米格尔 再也别回来了\N{\ren}You leave San Miguel and never come back for the rest of your days.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.96,0:32:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,乔 我已经照你要求弄好马车了\N{\ren}Eh, Joe, I have prepared the wagon the way you asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.72,0:32:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,后座有两副空棺\N{\ren}It's sitting out in the back here with two empty coffins.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.36,0:32:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你做好决定了吗？\N{\ren}What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.44,0:32:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要转行吗？\N{\ren}Are you changing your profession?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.70,0:32:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想谋生的话 最好转行\N{\ren}If you want to go on living, you'd better.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.28,0:32:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为你会是个很好的抬棺人\N{\ren}In my opinion, you'll make a fine pallbearer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.84,0:32:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,关了这家店 跟我一起走 好吗？\N{\ren}Close this place and come with me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.12,0:32:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,关店？好吧 我们去哪里呢？\N{\ren}Oh, close up, huh? It's done. Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.49,0:32:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道我们要去哪里 这要保密吗？\N{\ren}I'd like to know where we are going, or is it a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.87,0:32:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,去河边看一下那里的尸体\N{\ren}Down by the river. Have a look at some corpses down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.71,0:33:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,罗霍家族发出邀请 我们必须赴宴\N{\ren}The Rojos say come to dinner and we must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.59,0:33:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但我根本不想去\N{\ren}But I don't like it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.34,0:33:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,即使他们答应了我们的种种要求\N{\ren}even if they've granted all the guarantees we've demanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.18,0:33:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是要去 但别碰任何东西\N{\ren}We'll go along with it, but don't touch anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.14,0:34:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不能吃 不能喝\N{\ren}You mustn't eat. You mustn't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.84,0:34:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,擦亮眼睛 保持警惕\N{\ren}You just keep your eyes open and keep your wits about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.84,0:34:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定没有人看到我们？\N{\ren}Are you sure that nobody has seen us?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.20,0:34:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也许一两个鬼看见了\N{\ren}Only a ghost or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.36,0:34:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,呸呸呸 别拿鬼来开玩笑\N{\ren}Oh no no no. Don't joke about things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.32,0:34:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,最好是别招惹亡魂\N{\ren}Ghosts are better left where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.22,0:34:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来很适合这块地方\N{\ren}You look as though this place suits you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.40,0:34:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你再这样下去 你很快就会长眠于此\N{\ren}If you go on like this, you will soon be here permanently.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.36,0:35:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\ren}I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.52,0:35:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么河岸有那么多尸体\N{\ren}Why is it with all those bodies down
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.08,0:35:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你只埋这两具？\N{\ren}by the river we are just burying these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.30,0:35:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是要埋葬他们\N{\ren}We're not. We're not gonna bury them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.00,0:35:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你这话是什么意思？\N{\ren}What do you mean we're not burying them?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.50,0:35:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我们不是要埋葬他们\N{\ren}That's right. We're not gonna bury them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.44,0:35:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不埋葬他们 那我们用这些尸体干嘛？\N{\ren}If we are not going to bury them, what will we use them for?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.97,0:35:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要这么大费周章？\N{\ren}Why are we taking the trouble to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.66,0:35:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,死人有时很有用\N{\ren}The dead can be very useful sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.62,0:35:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不止一次帮我度过难关\N{\ren}They've helped me out of tough spots more than once.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.78,0:35:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,首先 死人不会说话\N{\ren}First, they don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.86,0:35:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,其次 如果我弄好了 他们看起来会像活人\N{\ren}Second, they can be made to look alive if I manage it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.14,0:35:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还有...\N{\ren}And, third...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.14,0:35:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你向他们开枪 不必担心\N{\ren}Well, third, if you shot them, there's no worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.44,0:35:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们已经死透了\N{\ren}'cause they're dead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.47,0:35:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗？\N{\ren}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.80,0:36:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都不明白 我要走了\N{\ren}It doesn't make a bit of sense to me, and I'm getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.26,0:36:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我还活着 就要跟活人呆一起 懂吗？\N{\ren}I'm alive, and I want to remain with the living, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.52,0:36:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等我死了 再跟死人呆一起吧\N{\ren}And when I'm dead, I'll want to remain with the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.48,0:36:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,强迫我与活人呆一起 我会不高兴的\N{\ren}I would be unhappy if somebody living forces me to remain with the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.35,0:36:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我说清楚了吧\N{\ren}I hope that's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.28,0:36:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 我也不喜欢你这样摆布尸体\N{\ren}And, also, I don't like the idea that you've placed those bodies there!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.99,0:36:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,葬在那里的人是这个不幸的小镇上  唯一死于肺炎的人\N{\ren}The man buried there is the only one who died of pneumonia in this cursed town!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.49,0:36:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点 好吗？\N{\ren}Take it easy, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.40,0:36:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这两个朋友会帮我付你的帐单\N{\ren}These two friends of ours here are gonna make me pay your bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.74,0:36:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,驾\N{\ren}Get up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.56,0:36:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们唯一能挑起战争的方式是...\N{\ren}The only reason they could have to start a war with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.32,0:37:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,把你从我身边绑走\N{\ren}would be to kidnap you from your husband's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.57,0:37:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这个罗霍太英勇了\N{\ren}He's gallant, this Rojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.62,0:37:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他担不起这样的恭维\N{\ren}I really didn't think him capable of compliments.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.58,0:37:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是 他的所言跟他的提议一样 都是虚伪的\N{\ren}And he's not. All that he says is false, like his proposals.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.46,0:37:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你们女人 如果事态简单 反而会疑神疑鬼\N{\ren}You women! If things aren't complicated for you, you become suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.42,0:37:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 因为在我看来就是不太对劲\N{\ren}Yes, because to me, it just didn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.43,0:37:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,太顺利了 我不相信他们\N{\ren}It went too smoothly. I don't trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.85,0:37:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你想证明我错了 是吗？\N{\ren}You'd like to prove me wrong, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.43,0:37:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一向如此\N{\ren}Always the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.35,0:37:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-晚安  -晚安\N{\ren}-Good night. -Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.19,0:38:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别怕 我不会伤害你的\N{\ren}Don't worry. I'm not gonna hurt ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.58,0:38:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想让你知道\N{\ren}I just want you to know why the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.34,0:38:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,罗霍家族急于和解的原因\N{\ren}Rojos want to make peace all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.96,0:38:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不久前有一队士兵  用马车载着黄金\N{\ren}You see, there was once a wagon load of gold that the soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.64,0:38:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,运往边境\N{\ren}were taking to the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.67,0:38:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰 快上来\N{\ren}John, come up here quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.55,0:38:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 但当丈夫在妻子卧室里发现一个男人时\N{\ren}Sorry, but when a husband finds a man in his wife's bedroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.43,0:38:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远想不到他会做出什么举动\N{\ren}you're never sure how he's gonna react.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.06,0:38:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-给他500元  -为什么？\N{\ren}-Give him $500. -How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.54,0:38:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,把钱给他\N{\ren}Give the money to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.10,0:39:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他有条有趣的消息 听他讲\N{\ren}He has an interesting story. Listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.73,0:39:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,消息可靠吗？你没搞错吧？\N{\ren}That's the right idea? You didn't misunderstand?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.86,0:39:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-只要我想我才会给出不可靠的消息 -雷蒙\N{\ren}-I get the wrong idea only when it suits me. -Ramon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.24,0:39:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么事？-护送金子的士兵\N{\ren}-What is it?  -The soldiers the ones who escorting the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.91,0:39:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有两个逃走了 躲在墓地里\N{\ren}Two of those soldiers got away. They are hiding out in the cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.74,0:39:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,巴克斯特正要去抓他们\N{\ren}The Baxters. They're about to capture them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.18,0:39:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,卢比奥 叫弟兄们集合\N{\ren}Rubio, et the men!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.80,0:39:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你的消息很灵通啊？\N{\ren}You are well informed, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.92,0:39:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种地方 要活命就得靠小道消息\N{\ren}A man's life in these parts often depends on a mere scrap of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.28,0:39:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥哥亲口说的\N{\ren}Your brother's own words.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.26,0:39:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,说 你为什么要帮我们？\N{\ren}Tell me. Why are you doing this for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.48,0:39:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,为了500元\N{\ren}$500.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.45,0:39:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要是这两个士兵出面指证雷蒙\N{\ren}With these two soldiers as witnesses against Ramon...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.36,0:39:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,政府就会端掉罗霍家族的势力了\N{\ren}the government will be able to rid the town of the Rojos and their whole band.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.22,0:39:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,到那时圣米格尔只有一个老大\N{\ren}Then San Miguel will have just one boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.82,0:39:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\ren}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.42,0:40:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\ren}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.32,0:40:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我们一起去吗？\N{\ren}Coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.64,0:40:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,当一个男人口袋里有了钱\N{\ren}When a man's got money in his pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.90,0:40:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他就开始欣赏和平\N{\ren}he begins to appreciate peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.90,0:40:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\ren}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.68,0:41:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,把马留在这里\N{\ren}Let's leave the horses here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.39,0:42:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看？\N{\ren}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.48,0:42:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\ren}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.56,0:42:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不对劲\N{\ren}There's something about it I don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.08,0:42:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一动不动 不像受伤 倒像假人\N{\ren}Too still to be wounded. More like dummies.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.03,0:42:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 罗霍巴不得是假人\N{\ren}Sure, dummies that are very interesting to the Rojos.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.30,0:42:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,最好藏起来 快点\N{\ren}Better hide. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.12,0:44:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该怎么办？\N{\ren}What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.34,0:44:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,带两个弟兄绕到两边开火\N{\ren}Take two men and circle around to the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.59,0:44:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量和他们周旋 好让我去干掉那两个人\N{\ren}Try to keep them busy long enough for me to get those two down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.88,0:45:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 去吧 快点\N{\ren}Go on. Go on. Quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.63,0:45:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护我 我去解决那两个人\N{\ren}Keep me covered. I am going to take care of those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.80,0:46:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 巴克斯特 如果你想要这两人 就带走吧\N{\ren}Listen, Baxter! You can have them now if you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.01,0:46:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,因为死人不会说话！\N{\ren}Since dead men can't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.11,0:46:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,看来他们不喜欢我这个玩笑\N{\ren}It seems they didn't like my joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.11,0:46:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,再过一会儿就放他们回家\N{\ren}We'll let them go home in a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.80,0:48:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好好招待这个坏小子...\N{\ren}We will keep this bad boy as our guest...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.56,0:48:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,直到巴克斯特离开圣米格尔 奔向边境\N{\ren}only until Baxter leaves San Miguel and heads for the frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.72,0:48:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,把他关在地窖\N{\ren}Put him in the cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.10,0:48:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,伊斯特班 干得好\N{\ren}Esteban, Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.90,0:48:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有了安东尼奥这个人质 巴克斯特一定得屈服\N{\ren}With Antonio as our prisoner, the Baxters have to give in to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.15,0:48:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们可以随意开条件了\N{\ren}Now we can make any kind of demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.74,0:48:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,米格尔阁下 米格尔阁下\N{\ren}Don Miguel! Don Miguel!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.28,0:48:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？还能说话吗？\N{\ren}What has happened? Talk, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.00,0:48:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 但有人向我开枪\N{\ren}I don't know, but somebody shot at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.56,0:49:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽索尔？\N{\ren}Marisol?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.60,0:49:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽索尔？\N{\ren}Marisol?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.48,0:49:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪 玛丽索尔？\N{\ren}Where are you, Marisol?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.22,0:49:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪 你总是在合适的时间出现在合适的地方\N{\ren}It's strange how you always manage to be in the right place at the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.24,0:49:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她伤势不严重 头疼会缓解的\N{\ren}It's nothing serious. A headache that will pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.00,0:49:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她要睡觉\N{\ren}She'll sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.50,0:49:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看着 不许让她离开房间半步 听到了吗？\N{\ren}Keep your eyes open. She's not to move from that room. You hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.72,0:49:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会跟任何人说是我带她来这里的\N{\ren}I wouldn't mention anything about me bringing her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.68,0:49:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让罗霍认为我站在你们这边\N{\ren}I wouldn't want the Rojos to think I was on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.06,0:50:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\ren}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.68,0:50:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是有钱的女人 我赏识用金钱收买的男人\N{\ren}I'm a woman who's rich enough to appreciate the men my money can buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.10,0:50:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经跟罗霍家族谈妥了\N{\ren}I've been to talk to the Rojos.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.94,0:50:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们愿意用安东尼奥换玛丽索尔\N{\ren}They'll give back Antonio in exchange for Marisol.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.12,0:50:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,时间定在明天上午\N{\ren}It'll take place in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.92,0:50:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你很快就会发财了\N{\ren}Very soon you are going to be rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.71,0:50:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我可不会为此而心碎\N{\ren}Yeah, and that's not gonna break my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.20,0:52:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪？你说我可以去见她的\N{\ren}Where is she? You said I'd be able to see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.38,0:52:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪？\N{\ren}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.08,0:52:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我要见她！\N{\ren}I wanna see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.38,0:52:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-回来 耶瑟 过来  -我想见！\N{\ren}-Come back here, Jesus. Come here. -I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.68,0:52:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见她 我想见她\N{\ren}I want to see her! I want to see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.34,0:52:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么不能见她呢？我想见她\N{\ren}Why can't I look at her? I want to see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.84,0:52:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 去他那里 玛丽索尔\N{\ren}Go. Go to him, Marisol.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.22,0:53:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\ren}Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.56,0:53:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-妈妈  -耶瑟\N{\ren}-Mama! -Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.18,0:54:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,胡里奥\N{\ren}Julio.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.38,0:54:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽索尔\N{\ren}Marisol.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.76,0:54:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,干掉胡里奥\N{\ren}Get Julio.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.66,0:54:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们警告过你 离开这个镇\N{\ren}You were warned to get out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.26,0:54:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我要给你做个了断\N{\ren}Now I'm gonna make you pay once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.97,0:54:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,别动他\N{\ren}Let him be!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.78,0:55:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好快走 雷蒙在等着\N{\ren}You better get goin'. Ramon's waitin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.48,0:55:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你 还不快带孩子回家\N{\ren}And, you, get that kid home where he belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.84,0:56:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙那个畜生\N{\ren}A pig, that Ramon.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.88,0:56:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙和他们有什么关系？\N{\ren}What's Ramon got to do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.54,0:56:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没人告诉你吗？\N{\ren}You weren't told, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.92,0:56:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这故事在这里流传很久了\N{\ren}In this part of the world, the story is very old.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.42,0:56:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,原本快乐的小家庭遇上了麻烦\N{\ren}A happy little family until trouble comes along.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.64,0:56:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而麻烦的名字就叫雷蒙\N{\ren}And trouble has the name of Ramon.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.30,0:56:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他声称玛丽莎的丈夫在赌博时出老千 根本没这回事\N{\ren}Claiming the husband cheated at cards, which wasn't true...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.14,0:56:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他把他的妻子抓来做人质 实则是同居\N{\ren}He gets the wife to live with him as hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.84,0:56:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那丈夫呢？\N{\ren}And the husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.32,0:56:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他？他什么都做不了\N{\ren}Him? There's nothing for him to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.66,0:56:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,罗霍威胁说要杀了他的儿子耶瑟...\N{\ren}The Rojos threatened to kill his little boy Jesus...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.08,0:56:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他只能接受现实\N{\ren}and he was forced to accept things.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.30,0:57:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那个雷蒙很聪明\N{\ren}That Ramon is smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.12,0:57:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪里？\N{\ren}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.76,0:57:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,向罗霍家族讨份工作\N{\ren}To the Rojos to look for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.06,0:57:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴美国佬站在我们这边\N{\ren}I am glad we have the americano with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.68,0:57:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们来说是最好的结果\N{\ren}It's the best thing that could have happened to us, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.70,0:57:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因为一旦政府要展开调查\N{\ren}'cause if either government starts an inquiry...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.56,0:57:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要大量地招兵买马\N{\ren}We'll need every man we can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.38,0:57:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道现在跟巴克斯特开战\N{\ren}I guess you know to be at war with the Baxters now...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.86,0:57:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,比坐在一箱炸药上还危险\N{\ren}is worse than sitting on a big case of dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.66,0:57:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-这个放哪里？-放在那里\N{\ren}-Where should we put this?  -Put it over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.52,0:57:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,来 大家一起干杯！\N{\ren}Come on, everybody! Drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.79,0:58:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好枪法 真是好枪法\N{\ren}Good shooting. Very good shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.25,0:58:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,想杀人时 一定得瞄准他的心脏\N{\ren}When you want to kill a man, you must shoot for his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.46,0:58:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而温切斯特是最好的武器\N{\ren}And the Winchester is the best weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.54,0:58:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好 但我还是喜欢我的点45口径手枪\N{\ren}That's very nice, but I'll stick with my a.45.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.10,0:58:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,当手持点45手枪的人  对决手持来福枪的人\N{\ren}When a man with a.45 meets a man with a rifle...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.64,0:58:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,拿手枪的人必死无疑\N{\ren}The man with the pistol will be a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.35,0:58:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一句墨西哥谚语 说得没错\N{\ren}That's an old Mexican proverb, and it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.89,0:58:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信吗？\N{\ren}You believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.22,0:58:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,帕奎托 派五个弟兄送玛丽索尔回小屋\N{\ren}Paquito, take five men and escort Marisol to the small house.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.48,0:58:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,直到我回去\N{\ren}Stay there till I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.75,0:59:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-一切都准备好了  -不要担心\N{\ren}-Everything's prepared. -Do not be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.08,0:59:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天就回去\N{\ren}I will return tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.13,0:59:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,马车都准备好了 我们可以走了\N{\ren}All the wagons are ready. We can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.88,0:59:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 我不在的时候玩尽兴点\N{\ren}Everyone, enjoy yourselves during my absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.52,0:59:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都听到雷蒙说的了 尽情享乐吧\N{\ren}You heard Ramon. Let's have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.52,1:00:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-他好重  -是的\N{\ren}-He weighs over a ton. -Of course...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.98,1:00:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他灌了那么多酒\N{\ren}with all he poured into himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.50,1:01:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\ren}Papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.97,1:01:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说任何人都不准见妈妈吗？\N{\ren}Did you not tell me no one could go see Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.64,1:01:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\ren}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.42,1:01:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么我不可以见 那男人却可以呢？\N{\ren}Then why does that man see her when I cannot?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.76,1:01:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要妈妈  -不要站在门口\N{\ren}-I want Mama. -Go away from the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.06,1:01:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我要妈妈\N{\ren}I want Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.58,1:01:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,安静点！\N{\ren}Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.68,1:01:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能被人发现\N{\ren}We cannot show ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.70,1:01:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须记住 不要靠近门口\N{\ren}You must remember that. You must stay away.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.92,1:01:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好\N{\ren}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.77,1:02:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在小屋那边开枪\N{\ren}There's somebody shooting up at the small house.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.60,1:02:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,立即备马 快去 我们走\N{\ren}Saddle the horses immediately! Come on. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.44,1:02:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小心！\N{\ren}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.27,1:03:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,给 拿着这些钱\N{\ren}Here you are. Now, take this money.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.94,1:03:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,够你们维持一段生活了 现在 穿过边境\N{\ren}It's enough to live on for a while. Now, get across the border.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.19,1:03:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,离圣米格尔越远越好\N{\ren}Get as much distance between yourselves and San Miguel as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.99,1:03:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该怎么感谢你？\N{\ren}How may we thank you for what you are doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.12,1:03:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 在罗霍家族来到之前赶快离开这里\N{\ren}Don't try. Just get goin' before the Rojos get here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.44,1:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么帮我们呢？\N{\ren}Why do you do this for us?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.79,1:04:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？因为我曾认识一个跟你很像的人\N{\ren}Why? 'Cause I knew someone like you once.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.98,1:04:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,却无人出手相助 现在 快走吧\N{\ren}There was no one there to help. Now, get movin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.52,1:04:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,离开这里\N{\ren}Get movin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.18,1:04:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,离开这里\N{\ren}Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.14,1:04:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 奇科？\N{\ren}What do you see, Chico?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.52,1:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们全死了 全被屠杀了\N{\ren}They're all dead. They massacred them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.06,1:05:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们绑架了玛丽索尔 -看上去是巴克斯特家族下的手\N{\ren}-They kidnapped Marisol! -Looks like the work of the Baxters.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.82,1:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快 要赶在他们袭击我们的大本营前回去\N{\ren}Quick, let's get back before they attack our house and the town.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.35,1:07:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,奇科 你去分发武器\N{\ren}Chico, give out the ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.06,1:07:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,伊斯特班 在房子周边布置人手 提高警惕\N{\ren}Esteban, spread your men around the house. Keep your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.07,1:07:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,米格尔 帕克 文森特 马丁 到后面去\N{\ren}Miguel, Paco, Vincente, Martin, behind the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.19,1:07:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,马诺洛和阿瓦罗 跟我来 警惕点\N{\ren}Manolo and Alvaro, come with me. Stay alert.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.16,1:07:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,根据屋内死者的情况看来 他们一定人多势众\N{\ren}The way they killed the men in the small house, there must be a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.80,1:07:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个和煦的夜晚\N{\ren}It's a warm evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.32,1:07:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们其中一辆马车轮子坏了\N{\ren}One of our wagons lost a wheel,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.26,1:07:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要回来找帮手\N{\ren}so we had to turn back here to get help.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.47,1:07:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有人告诉我...\N{\ren}One of the men tells me...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.70,1:07:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,巴克斯特袭击了小屋\N{\ren}the Baxters attacked the small house.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.26,1:07:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这件事吗？\N{\ren}Do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.48,1:07:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你掌握的情况\N{\ren}Tell me what you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.56,1:08:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,说\N{\ren}Well?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.01,1:08:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你把玛丽索尔藏哪了？\N{\ren}Where did you hide Marisol?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.82,1:08:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,卢比奥\N{\ren}Rubio.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.96,1:08:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你口渴了 想喝水吗？\N{\ren}You are thirsty. You want to drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.30,1:08:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,喝太急了 根本没喝到\N{\ren}No, no, it is too soon to drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.94,1:09:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把他带过来\N{\ren}Bring him over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.72,1:09:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你就像一个顽固的白痴\N{\ren}You're behaving like a stubborn idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.44,1:09:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我们玛丽索尔在哪\N{\ren}Tell us where Marisol is...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.84,1:09:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一切就了结了\N{\ren}and it will all be ended!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.42,1:09:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一个星期后你就康复了 想去哪就去哪\N{\ren}In a week, you'll be back in shape. You can go wherever you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.72,1:09:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,今天到此为止\N{\ren}That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.30,1:09:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他迟早得开口 只是时间的问题\N{\ren}Sooner or later, he'll talk. It's just a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.40,1:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,注意别让他跑了或死了 其余你们看着办\N{\ren}Watch out he doesn't escape or die otherwise. Do what you like.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.12,1:10:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,最好等他恢复知觉 他现在什么也感觉不到\N{\ren}And wait till he comes to. This way, he hardly feels anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.18,1:10:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个牌局等了三天了\N{\ren}I've had a poker hand waiting three days.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.62,1:10:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在却被困在这里看守这个美国白痴\N{\ren}Now I'm stuck here! I can't get to it while I'm guarding this americano idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.20,1:10:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你会发觉这比打牌更好玩\N{\ren}I think you will find this more amusing than cards.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.46,1:10:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,别把他搞死就行\N{\ren}All orders are to be sure he does not die...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.66,1:10:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但也要让他后悔投胎\N{\ren}and also make sure he regrets the day he was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.06,1:11:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那个外国佬睡着了\N{\ren}The gringo is asleep, I imagine.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.70,1:11:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 我会享受叫醒他的\N{\ren}That's all right. I'll enjoy waking him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.56,1:12:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-伊斯特班 那是什么声音？-我不知道\N{\ren}-Esteban, what was that noise?  -I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.90,1:12:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到一声大叫 然后是撞击声\N{\ren}I heard a yell, and then a crash.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.10,1:12:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,再躲也没用\N{\ren}It's useless to hide.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.28,1:12:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你耍不了小聪明了\N{\ren}You're finished playing the smart boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.14,1:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,上阁楼看看\N{\ren}Go up and look in the loft.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.54,1:13:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,酒桶后面也别放过\N{\ren}And take a look behind the barrels!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.68,1:13:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们离开这里\N{\ren}Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.32,1:13:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快！快点！\N{\ren}Hurry! Quick!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.94,1:13:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快点泼水 喂 你跟我来\N{\ren}Hurry with that water! Hey, you, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.12,1:13:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,包围城镇 封锁所有街道出口\N{\ren}Surround the town! Block all the streets leading out!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.84,1:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,给我找到他\N{\ren}Find him for me!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.13,1:13:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-伊斯特班 搜查全镇  -跟我来\N{\ren}-Esteban, search the whole town. -Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.64,1:14:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻把他找回来 不管什么代价\N{\ren}Get him back right now! You've got to at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.16,1:14:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看看马厩 看看所有畜栏和库房\N{\ren}Look in the stables, in every corral, in the stores!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.06,1:14:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还有教堂\N{\ren}Look for him in the church!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.12,1:14:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,到那儿看看 不准放过任何角落\N{\ren}Go in there! Search every inch of it!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.78,1:14:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不要遗漏\N{\ren}Search everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.74,1:14:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,卢比奥 进来\N{\ren}Rubio, in here!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.02,1:14:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哪户人匿藏他 就烧了他的房子\N{\ren}If somebody is hiding him, burn their house down...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.08,1:14:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,像宰狗一样把他们宰了\N{\ren}and kill them like dogs!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.08,1:14:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你们 上那\N{\ren}You, up here!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.16,1:14:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在巴克斯特地界找找 要活捉\N{\ren}Look for him near the Baxters, but I want him alive!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.20,1:14:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,活捉！\N{\ren}Alive!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.25,1:14:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,卢比奥 去酒馆\N{\ren}Rubio, in the bar.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.07,1:15:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他什么都不知道 他在耍花样\N{\ren}He says he knows nothing. He's trying to be smart.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.62,1:15:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,带到我这里来\N{\ren}Bring him here to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.64,1:15:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-我说的实话  -你什么都不知道 是吗？\N{\ren}-I'm telling the truth. -Well, you know nothing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.58,1:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-我没看见他 -卢比奥 你搞定他\N{\ren}-I'm not cheating. -Rubio, you take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.76,1:16:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他藏哪里了？\N{\ren}Where have you hidden him?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.10,1:16:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有藏匿他\N{\ren}I didn't hide him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.38,1:16:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟那个卑劣的美国佬做朋友\N{\ren}You're the right friend for that filthy americano.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.70,1:16:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你的下场会跟他一样\N{\ren}You'll end up the same way.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.65,1:16:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们找遍了所有地方\N{\ren}We looked everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.74,1:16:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,地窖 阁楼 房顶\N{\ren}In his cellar, in the attic, on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.57,1:16:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但什么踪迹都没有\N{\ren}There is no trace.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.78,1:16:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,后面房间也没人\N{\ren}I couldn't find anybody in the back room.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.87,1:16:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他肯定是向巴克斯特寻求庇护了\N{\ren}I'm certain he has taken refuge with the Baxters.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.00,1:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那个美国佬不蠢 他知道那边是最好的藏身之地\N{\ren}The americano isn't stupid. He knows that's the best place to hide.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.75,1:16:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,巴克斯特家族？\N{\ren}The Baxters, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.76,1:16:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,最好去抓住他\N{\ren}Then better go and get him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.78,1:16:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是做他朋友的下场\N{\ren}And that's for being his friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.24,1:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,天杀的\N{\ren}Curse them.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.88,1:17:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,皮里佩洛\N{\ren}Piripero?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.04,1:17:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,皮里佩洛\N{\ren}Piripero?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.24,1:17:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-过来  -我没看到人\N{\ren}-Come here. -I can't see anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.06,1:17:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这里\N{\ren}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.84,1:18:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你在里面干什么？\N{\ren}What are you doing in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.06,1:18:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,别管了 帮我离开这里\N{\ren}Never mind. Get me out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.88,1:18:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但你还没死呢\N{\ren}But you're not dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.20,1:18:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不帮我离开这里 我就会死 快\N{\ren}I will be if you don't get me out of here, quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.72,1:18:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,把盖放下\N{\ren}Get that lid down.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.00,1:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,卢比奥！\N{\ren}Rubio!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.32,1:20:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,还有人活着\N{\ren}I see some signs of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.34,1:20:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好 他们会随时出来\N{\ren}Let's be ready when they decide to come out.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.16,1:20:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开枪 我们投降\N{\ren}Don't shoot! We surrender!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.04,1:20:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！别开枪！我们出来！\N{\ren}Stop! Don't shoot! We're coming out!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.76,1:20:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-我投降！别开枪!  -别开枪！\N{\ren}-I surrender! Hold back your fire! -Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.44,1:20:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们投降\N{\ren}We surrender!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.48,1:21:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\ren}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.42,1:21:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见证这一幕\N{\ren}I wanna take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.83,1:22:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙 别开枪！我们就出来\N{\ren}Ramon, don't shoot! We're coming out!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.14,1:22:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们投降\N{\ren}We surrender!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.94,1:22:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 你们赢了 够了\N{\ren}Listen, you've won. It's enough!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.05,1:22:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我会离开小镇 你要我怎样做都行\N{\ren}I'll get out of town! I'll do whatever you like!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.72,1:23:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-你保证？-我发誓 雷蒙\N{\ren}-You promise that?  -I swear it! Ramon.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.84,1:23:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会又耍什么花样吧？\N{\ren}You won't try a trick of any kind?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.30,1:23:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不会 不耍花样\N{\ren}None! No, no tricks!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.90,1:23:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过了 我保证我们会离开的\N{\ren}I said before, I give you my word. We'll leave!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.36,1:23:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗？你最好先征求你太太的同意\N{\ren}Are you sure? You had better ask permission of your wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.78,1:23:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也许她不太乐意\N{\ren}Maybe she won't be too happy!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.28,1:23:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,安东尼奥！\N{\ren}Antonio!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.14,1:23:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰！\N{\ren}John!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.40,1:24:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手\N{\ren}Murderers.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.44,1:24:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有持枪\N{\ren}They had no guns.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.08,1:24:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手！你们下地狱去吧\N{\ren}Murderers! I hope you rot in hell!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.25,1:24:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们兄弟将血债血偿！我诅咒你们！\N{\ren}May you and your brothers die spitting blood! Curse you for this!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.58,1:24:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手！\N{\ren}Murderers!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.10,1:24:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走 好戏已经结束了\N{\ren}Let's go. The show's over anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.82,1:24:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,继续找他 在尸堆里找\N{\ren}Keep looking for him. Search among those bodies.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.80,1:24:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那个美国佬肯定在某个地方\N{\ren}The filthy americano has to be somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.88,1:27:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,西尔瓦尼托？\N{\ren}Silvanito?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.31,1:27:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,西尔瓦尼托在哪儿？\N{\ren}Where's Silvanito?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.64,1:27:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有什么消息吗？\N{\ren}Any news today?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.18,1:27:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我得告诉你一些坏消息\N{\ren}I have to tell you some news that's pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.11,1:27:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想告诉你这些 但... \N{\ren}-I hate to tell you this, Joe, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.82,1:27:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,西尔瓦尼托呢？\N{\ren}Where is Silvanito?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.84,1:27:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,西尔瓦尼托？他今早被拉蒙的人抓住了\N{\ren}Silvanito? He was captured this morning by those men of Ramon's.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.22,1:27:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在镇外抓住他的 他当时正往矿洞这边走\N{\ren}They grabbed him outside the village. He was on his way to this mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.32,1:27:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他本来要带一些补给品来 现在却被雷蒙抓走了\N{\ren}He was bringing in some provisions. Ramon's got him now.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.46,1:27:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他被严刑拷打 但他不会说的\N{\ren}He's being tortured, but he won't talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.50,1:27:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我很了解他 他是顽强的人\N{\ren}I know him well. He's a stubborn man.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.56,1:27:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不管他们怎样折磨他 就算丢了命他也不会说的\N{\ren}No matter what they do, he won't say a word, even if it means his life.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.64,1:27:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 他们绝不可能逼他就范的\N{\ren}Listen to me. They'll never be able to force him.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.82,1:28:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你这老顽固 快开口说吧\N{\ren}Now, fool, loosen up your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.54,1:28:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-休想 -卢比奥！\N{\ren}-No! -Rubio!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.04,1:28:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好回你的店里去 老头\N{\ren}You better get back to your shop, old man.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.58,1:28:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-你就快有生意上门了  -啊 太好了\N{\ren}-You're liable to have some business. -Ah, very good!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.64,1:28:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我就想听这句话\N{\ren}That's what I wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.50,1:28:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我还为你带来了一份小惊喜\N{\ren}And I have a little surprise for you that I brought along.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.82,1:28:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你很需要它\N{\ren}I know how much you'll need it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.72,1:28:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我费了很大的劲才弄到手的\N{\ren}It was very hard to get my hands on.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.62,1:28:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次动脑筋 没有人能抗拒两桶酒的\N{\ren}I got it by first using my head. No one can resist two barrels of wine.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.20,1:28:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗？然后我想...\N{\ren}Isn't that right? Then I thought that...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.84,1:28:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能需要那把枪 我还带来了另一份礼物\N{\ren}well, you might need that pistol, and I brought another present.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.32,1:28:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,炸药 我从罗霍家族偷来的\N{\ren}It's dynamite. I stole it from the Rojos.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.88,1:28:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我看现在是你点燃导火线的时机了\N{\ren}And now it seems to me the moment's come for you to light the fuse...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.98,1:28:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,把炸药送回给他们\N{\ren}and send it back to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.34,1:29:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,天还挺亮\N{\ren}Still lots of light.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.88,1:29:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在睡觉还太早了\N{\ren}Too early to be asleep yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.58,1:29:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,卢比奥 枪给我\N{\ren}Rubio, here.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.64,1:29:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想糟蹋这把来复枪 再也找不到一把这么好的了\N{\ren}I shouldn't like to ruin the rifle. I could never find another like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.50,1:29:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 雷蒙 我们来试试这个\N{\ren}Listen, Ramon, let's try it with this one now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.70,1:31:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,外国佬！\N{\ren}Gringo!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.38,1:31:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你想见我\N{\ren}Heard you wanted to see me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.36,1:31:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,美国佬死定了\N{\ren}The americano's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.16,1:32:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把那位老人家放下来\N{\ren}Let the old man down.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.10,1:32:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 雷蒙？\N{\ren}What's wrong, Ramon?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.06,1:32:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么没打到呢？\N{\ren}You losing your touch?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.36,1:32:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你在害怕吗 雷蒙？\N{\ren}Are you afraid, Ramon?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.56,1:32:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"想杀人时 一定得瞄准心脏"\N{\ren}"You shoot to kill, you better hit the heart."
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.08,1:32:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己说的 雷蒙\N{\ren}Your own words. Ramon.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.38,1:33:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,心脏 雷蒙\N{\ren}The heart. Ramon.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.40,1:33:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘记瞄准心脏\N{\ren}Don't forget the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.60,1:33:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄准心脏 否则你是无法阻止我的\N{\ren}Aim for the heart or you'll never stop me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.82,1:34:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,当手持点45手枪的人  对决手持来福枪的人\N{\ren}When a man with a.45 meets a man with a rifle...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.02,1:34:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你说拿手枪的人必死无疑\N{\ren}You said the man with the pistol's a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.56,1:34:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看看是不是真的\N{\ren}Let's see if that's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.58,1:35:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,动手啊 子弹上膛开枪吧\N{\ren}Go ahead, load up and shoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.22,1:37:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 听着 乔\N{\ren}Hey, listen, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.70,1:37:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我...\N{\ren}Listen, l-l...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.66,1:38:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你们政府会很高兴拿回黄金的\N{\ren}Well, guess your government will be glad to see that gold back.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.98,1:38:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\ren}And you,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.68,1:38:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想留在这里等他们来吧？\N{\ren}you don't want to be here when they get it, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.02,1:38:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说墨西哥政府在一边\N{\ren}You mean the Mexican government on one side...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.24,1:38:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,美国政府在另一边？\N{\ren}and maybe the Americans on the other side?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.74,1:38:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我 就在中间？\N{\ren}Me, right smack in the middle?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.28,1:38:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 太危险了\N{\ren}Mm-mmm. Too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.46,1:38:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了\N{\ren}So long.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.78,1:38:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\ren}Adios.
